high_descs: Pick up the tomato on the counter to the left of the stove.
Turn right and walk straight to the sink.
Place the tomato in the sink, wash the tomato and remove it.
With the tomato, walk to the coffee maker to you right.
Place the clean tomato next to the knife on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean tomato on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the wall, then turn right and walk up to the counter
Pick up the tomato off of the counter to the left of the stove.
Turn right and walk over to the sink.
Put the tomato in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and then remove the tomato.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn left to face the counter.
Put the clean tomato on the counter in front of the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean tomato on the counter.

high_descs: Go straight across the kitchen towards the stove.
Pick up the tomato between the egg and the sponge, on the counter to the left of the stove.
Turn to your right and go to the sink ahead of you.
Place the tomato in the sink, turn the water on, rinse off the tomato, turn the water off, and remove the tomato from the sink.
Move over to the counter to the right of the sink, on your right.
Place the tomato between the potato and the butter knife, on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a  clean tomato on the counter.
